asset.author: Volcom
asset.hookText: I was up in Portland for a few days in June with Grant Taylor and Collin Provost. We spent the days driving around town attempting to shoot photos, but ultimately we ended up shredding some good parks as well. We started out the days at Glenhaven and Battleground (this one is in Washington), but due to rain we were forced to skate indoors at the Department of Skateboarding too. All was good fun.
